      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "72a4ad71c9:20",
      "text": "这个 primvar 设置并控制 bulb 的基础 glow color。",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "72a4ad71c9:21",
      "text": "我们还使用这个 primvar 驱动 glass refraction color",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "72a4ad71c9:24",
      "text": "这个 primvar 设置并控制 bulb glow gain 的初始 intensity。",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 10
